ibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:18:344\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">18.344</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:7:82\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">7.82</biblScope> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">τῶ κε . . αἶψα μεταστρέψειε νόον μετὰ σὸν καὶ ἐμὸν κ.</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:15:52\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">15.52</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">θαλέων ἐμπλησάμενος κ.</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:22:504\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">22.504</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:19:319\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">19.319</biblScope> </bibl>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">τοῦ δ᾽ οὔ ποτε κυδάλιμον κ. ταρβεῖ</foreign>, of a boar or lion, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:12:45\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">12.45</biblScope> </bibl>: dat. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">κῆρι</foreign> as <pos opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"pos\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Adv.\">Adv.</a></pos>, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">with all the heart, heartily</tr_>, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ὅν τε Ζεὺς κῆρι φιλήσῃ</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:9:117\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">9.117</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>: mostly strengthd., <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">περὶ κ. φιλεῖν 